episodes.title: Iki-jigoku! Rufi Kutsujoku no Dai Tankutsu-jo
episodes.plot: After his defeat, Luffy is sent to a prison in the Udon region. Kiku returns to the mountain where Oden Castle was destroyed and discovers that the group there managed to escape the destruction.

episodes.title: The Holyland in Tumult! Emperor of the Sea Blackbeard Cackles!
episodes.plot: Perona learns from a newspaper that Gecko Moria is alive and prepares to leave Kuraigana Island to search for him. Moria and his zombie army attack Pirate Island to find Absalom only to learn that he had been killed.

episodes.title: Ugokidasu - Dato Kaido Daikeikaku!
episodes.plot: Dogstorm clashes with Shutenmaru, who refuses to aid in Kin'emon's operation. Sanji and the others seek out recruits.

episodes.title: Rampage! The Prisoners - Luffy and Kid!
episodes.plot: Nami and Shinobu finish with their current objective in the Flower Capital and Sanji's soba stand is growing more popular. In Udon, Luffy and Kid continue to work. The angry vice warden tries to attack them only to be defeated by the pair.

episodes.title: Dai Hyoban! Sanji no Ohako Soba!
episodes.plot: Sanji tangles with some gang members who disrupt his soba business and learns that one of his customers has friends in high places.

episodes.title: Goka Kenran - Wano Kuni Ichi no Bijo: Komurasaki
episodes.plot: Wano's most popular courtesan heads to the palace, but a revenge plot threatens the proceedings.

episodes.title: A Tale of Chivalry! Zoro and Tonoyasu's Little Trip!
episodes.plot: Zoro goes to a gambling house with Tonoyasu. Meanwhile, the Ninja-Pirate-Mink-Samurai Alliance works to steal weapons and food. Franky learns that Minatomo no longer has the blueprints of Kaido's mansion.

episodes.title: A State of Emergency! Big Mom Closes in!
episodes.plot: The banquet at Orochi's palace begins . Shinobu, Nami, and Brook sneak into the palace as well. Meanwhile, in Udon prison, Kid explains to Luffy and Caribou about how he lost his arm.

episodes.title: The Capital in an Uproar! Another Assassin Targets Sanji!
episodes.plot: King flies to the waterfall while the Big Mom Pirates are coming up and knocks their ship down. Meanwhile, back at the capital, Page One attack multiple soba shops and owners looking for Sanji.

episodes.title: Dashing! The Righteous Soba Mask!
episodes.plot: As he confronts Page One, Sanji puts on his Raid Suit and displays its capabilities. Back in the shogun's caste, Robin was sneaking around trying to find important information.

episodes.title: Zettai Zetsumei - Kyoi no Orochi Oniwabanshu
episodes.plot: Robin gets caught by the Orochi Oniwabanshu in Orochi's castle. The ninjas attack Robin in order to find the truth of her intentions. Meanwhile, Chopper, Kiku, Tama, and Momonosuke find Big Mom at the shore after the encounter with King.

episodes.title: Shura-jo! Osoreru Daija Shogun Orochi
episodes.plot: At Kuri Beach, Chopper gives the amnesiac Big Mom a fake name. Back inside the shogun's castle, Orochi warns his guests about the return of the Scabbards. Toko laughs, enraging Orochi. As Orochi lashes out at Toko, Komurasaki steps in.

episodes.title: The Flower Falls! The Final Moment of the Most Beautiful Woman in the Land of Wano!
episodes.plot: Orochi takes his rage out on Komurasaki as Robin protects Toko. Brook, Nami, and Shinobu arrive at the banquet hall to aid Robin. Right after Orochi releases his grip on Komurasaki during the commotion, Kyoshiro cuts her down.

episodes.title: The Bond Between Prisoners! Luffy and Old Man Hyo!
episodes.plot: In the Ringo region, Kanjuro meets up with Shinobu's group. In Ebisu Town, Law's group learns from a newspaper that a funeral for Komurasaki will be held and that Kid escaped from Udon prison.

episodes.title: A Lead Performer! Queen the Plague Emerges!
episodes.plot: Luffy kicks Daifugo to defend Hyogoro and then fights the guards until Babanuki fires a cannonball at him. Raizo manages to steal some keys from the Prisoner Mines executive tower. Later Queen arrives at the Udon prison.

episodes.title: Goes up. Luffy's Desperate Escape!
episodes.plot: At the Prisoner Mines, the Sumo Inferno begins, but Luffy easily defeated his opponents. Meanwhile at the Flower Capital bathhouse, Drake and Hawkins arrive to search for those associated with the Kozuki Family.

episodes.title: Dead or Alive! Queen's Sumo Inferno!
episodes.plot: At the Prisoner Mines, the Sumo Inferno begins, but Luffy easily defeated his opponents. Meanwhile at the Flower Capital bathhouse, Drake and Hawkins arrive to search for those associated with the Kozuki Family.

episodes.title: Gyukimaru! Zoro Fights a Duel on Bandit's Bridge
episodes.plot: Sumo Inferno continues and Queen sends in the Gifters. At the bridge, Zoro clashes with Gyukimaru to get Shusui back. Their fight is interrupted when a woman and Toko arrive seeking help as they were chased by an assassin known as Kamazo.

episodes.title: A Big Turnover! The Three-Sword Style Overcomes Danger!
episodes.plot: During an argument with Shinobu, Law plans to rescue his crew. Meanwhile at Oihagi Bridge, Zoro continues his clash with Kamazo.

episodes.title: Zoro, Stunned! The Shocking Identity of the Mysterious Woman!
episodes.plot: Luffy continues trying to use an advanced Busoshoku Haki technique as he and Hyogoro are confronted by Alpacaman and Madilloman.

episodes.title: Get the Hang of It! The Land of Wano's Haki - Ryuo!
episodes.plot: After Hiyori reveals her identity to Zoro, she explains about some things about her past such as how Kawamatsu watched over her after her parents' death.

episodes.title: Tonoyasu! Ebisu's most beloved!
episodes.plot: Luffy tries to learn Ryuo through fighting in the Sumo Inferno. It continues until the night and will resume the next day. Luffy and Hyogoro meet Caribou and Raizo and talks about the rebellion.

episodes.title: Shaking the nation. The identity of Ushimitsu Kozo
episodes.plot: After his capture, Tonoyasu is sentenced to execution. Meanwhile, Holdem and his men battle the Mt. Atama Thieves. While clashing with Ashura Doji, Holdem sets the mountain on fire.

episodes.title: The Straw Hats are running! Save the captive Tonoyasu
episodes.plot: Toko and Zoro's group make their way to the Flower Capital. As Shimotsuki Yasuie is placed on a wooden pole and is being broadcast throughout Wano, his old acquaintances recognize him.

episodes.title: Zoro's Fury! The Truth About the Smile!
episodes.plot: After claiming responsibility for Kin'emon's secret message, saying it was a prank, and casting doubt in the Rasetsu prison guards, Yasuie meets a brutal end as Orochi and his men shoot him to death.

episodes.title: Toko's Tears! Orochi's Pitiless Bullets!
episodes.plot: As the citizens of Ebisu Town grieve over Yasuie's death, Shinobu reveals more information about the SMILE fruits. Meanwhile Zoro and Sanji step in fight to save Toko from Orochi.

episodes.title: The Straw Hats Step In! An Uproarious Deadly Battle at the Execution Ground!
episodes.plot: Zoro and Sanji start fighting against Orochi's clan. Nami and the rest of the Straw Hats join them. Meanwhile, at the Excavation Labor Camp a new criminal has arrived. And a shocking truth is revealed.

episodes.title: Luffy's Determination! Win Through the Sumo Inferno!
episodes.plot: Zoro clashes with Kyoshiro and Sanji clashes with X Drake while Usopp takes Toko to safety. Right after that the Orochi Oniwabanshu arrives to confront the Straw Hat Pirates.

episodes.title: The Coming of the Storm! Big Mom's Great Rampage!
episodes.plot: After the skirmish inside the Flower Capital, Kin'emon confesses to Ashura Doji that he provoked Holdem into attacking Mt. Atama. When Ashura becomes angry, Kin'emon admits his mistake and once again begs him for his help.

episodes.title: A Grudge Over Oshiruko - Luffy Gets into a Desperate Situation
episodes.plot: Big Mom subdues Queen when the latter tries to fight her. During that scuffle, Kid and Killer are saved from drowning. Big Mom does not find any oshiruko, and when Luffy blurts out that he ate it, she attacks him out of rage.

episodes.title: Stop the Emperor of the Sea! Queen's Secret Plan!
episodes.plot: Luffy attempts to defend against Big Mom's attack, but she sends him and Hyogoro crashing into a wall. They both survived, but Big Mom continues attacking Luffy, chasing him around the Prisoner Mines.

episodes.title: The Ultimate Weapon! Excite Bullets Aimed at Luffy
episodes.plot: Right after Big Mom regains her memories, she suddenly faints. Queen quickly orders to restrain Big Mom and escorts her to Onigashima. With both Queen and Big Mom away, Luffy continues practicing with advanced Busoshoku Haki.

episodes.title: Start Fighting Back! Luffy and the Red Scabbard Samurai!
episodes.plot: Raizo freed Kawamastsu and with Luffy, Chopper, Kiku and Hyogoro they start fighting the Hundred Beast Pirates of the Udon prison meanwhile zoro and Hyori got attacked by Fukurokoji's underlings.

episodes.title: We're Here to Win! Luffy's Desperate Scream!
episodes.plot: Luffy and his group continue to rebel against the prison guards, however, the prisoners attempt to stop them after the plague spreads rapidly. Luffy takes drastic action in an attempt to win the prisoner's faith and stir them to rebel too.

episodes.title: Warriors' Dream! Luffy's Conquer of Udon!
episodes.plot: After Udon is conquered, Chopper tends to Luffy and works to develop a cure for his condition. Luffy asks Kid to join the fight against Kaido, but Kid rejects his offer and leaves Udon with Killer.

episodes.title: Orochi's Pursuers! Ninja Army Corps vs. Zoro
episodes.plot: Zoro is continuously pursued by Orochi's ninjas. Law strikes a deal with Basil Hawkins in regards to the freedom of The Heart Pirates.

episodes.title: Tension Rises in Onigashima! Two Emperors of the Sea Meet?!
episodes.plot: Kanjuro, Nami, and Franky travel across Wano. Brook, Ussop, and Robin also travel Wano using a dock. Ashura reveals ships that he has that will be used for the assault on Onigashima. Zoro battles for his sword. Big Mom and Kaidio meet.

episodes.title: Hiyori's Confession! Reunion on Oihagi Bridge
episodes.plot: Big Mom and Kadio come to blows leaving Kadio's subordinate nervous. Reunions take place as Hyogoro and the yakuza bosses from the past get reacquainted while across Wano, Hiyori and Kawamatsu also reunite.

episodes.title: Its Name is Enma! Oden's Meito!
episodes.plot: Kawamatsu tells Hiyori how he and a fox named Onimaru defended and collected weapons belonging to the dead. Hiyori offers Zoro Enma, the legendary sword said to have cut Kadio.

episodes.title: "A New Alliance?! Kaido's Army Gathers"
episodes.plot: Zoro agrees to return Shusui in exchange for Enma, Law subdues Hawkins and escapes. At Onigashima, Kaidou and Big Mom decide to put aside their feud and form an alliance to conquer the world.

episodes.title: Ticking Down to the Great Battle! The Straw Hats Go into Combat Mode!
episodes.plot: Zoro receives Enma and sees its destructive power. Luffy continues training his Busoshoku Haki.
